{
  "title": "ISic000108. Dedication for a local patron by the decurions",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Tuuli Ahlholm, Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"yrim\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">yriṃ</span> [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span><span data-text=\"pa\n                    \" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">pa-]<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span></span>  <span data-text=\"tr\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">[tr]</span>  <span data-text=\"ono\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">ono</span>  <span data-text=\"optimo\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">[optimo]</span>  <span data-text=\"or\n                    do\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"\">[or-]<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[d]o</span>  <span data-text=\"dec\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"\">dec</span>  <span data-text=\"urion\n                    \" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"\">[urion-]<br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span></span>  <span data-text=\"u\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"\">[u]</span>  <span data-text=\"m\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"\">m</span>  <span data-text=\"pecunia\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"\">pecun[ia]</span>  <span data-text=\"publica\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"\">[pub(lica)]</span>  <span data-text=\"ob\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"\">[ob]</span>  <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"multa\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"\">multa</span>  <span data-text=\"merita\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"\">merị[ta]</span>  <span data-text=\"er\n                    ga\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"\">[er-]<br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>g̣a</span>  <span data-text=\"rem\" data-n=\"95\" data-lemma=\"\">rem</span>  <span data-text=\"publicam\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"\">public[am]</span>  <span data-text=\"fecit\" data-n=\"105\" data-lemma=\"\">[f(ecit)]</span>  <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span><span data-text=\"ex\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"\">ex</span>  <span data-text=\"decreto\" data-n=\"115\" data-lemma=\"\">d(ecreto)</span>  <span data-text=\"decurionum\" data-n=\"120\" data-lemma=\"\">d(ecurionum)</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Tuuli Ahlholm, Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"yrim\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">YRI.</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span><span data-text=\"pa\n                    \" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">..]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span></span><span data-text=\"tr\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">[..]</span><span data-text=\"ono\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">ONO</span><span data-text=\"optimo\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">[......</span><span data-text=\"or\n                    do\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"\">..]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[.]O</span><span data-text=\"dec\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"\">DEC</span><span data-text=\"urion\n                    \" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"\">[.....]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span></span><span data-text=\"u\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"\">[.]</span><span data-text=\"m\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"\">M</span><span data-text=\"pecunia\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"\">PECUN[..</span><span data-text=\"publica\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"\">....</span><span data-text=\"ob\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"\">..]</span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"multa\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"\">MULTA</span><span data-text=\"merita\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"\">MER.[..</span><span data-text=\"er\n                    ga\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"\">..]<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>.A</span><span data-text=\"rem\" data-n=\"95\" data-lemma=\"\">REM</span><span data-text=\"publicam\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"\">PUBLIC[..</span><span data-text=\"fecit\" data-n=\"105\" data-lemma=\"\">..]</span><br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span><span data-text=\"ex\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"\">EX</span><span data-text=\"decreto\" data-n=\"115\" data-lemma=\"\">D</span><span data-text=\"decurionum\" data-n=\"120\" data-lemma=\"\">D</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic000108_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2022-07-08\" src=\"ISic000108_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000108.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2022-07-08\" src=\"ISic000108-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic000108_right_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2022-07-08\" src=\"ISic000108_right_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000108_right.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2022-07-08\" src=\"ISic000108_right-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic000108_top_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2022-07-08\" src=\"ISic000108_top_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000108_top.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2022-07-08\" src=\"ISic000108_top-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic000108_base_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2022-07-08\" src=\"ISic000108_base_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000108_base.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J.Prag 2022-07-08\" src=\"ISic000108_base-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text from autopsy, read against Bivona (1994)</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Bivona (1994) asserts an unclear 'm' at the end of the visible line 1, but 'a' is equally possible.</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"6\">6: <span>Bivona (1994) reads 'ga' at the beginning of the visible line 6, but the 'g' is heavily obscured; potentially an 's' instead.</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou</a></p>  <p>[---] the most excellent patron. The order of decurions built [this] with public money, on account of his many merits directed towards the state, by decree of the decurions.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>As stressed by Bivona (1994, 140-141) the top line(s) likely mentioned the recipient of the dedication. Although Bivona (1994) makes extensive restorations, they fit the dimensions of the stone and make sense of the immensely fragmentary text.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 1994.0773 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</a>  </li><li> Belvedere 1982 37 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002161\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002161</a>  </li><li> Bivona 1994 26 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Text is lightly carved. Visible serifs. Letter spacing and size is consistent, except for final line which is inconsistent with the rest of the inscription.</p> Line 1  53-54  Line 2  51-56  Line 3  53-54  Line 4  47-48  Line 5  39-45  Line 6  41-42  Line 7  48-53  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
